{"tid":1531402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Roadblock手足/司機/專業人士請入","createTime":"2019-09-02T08:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T13:57:33.000Z","uid":46781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e9a9123a2b17d238df1e02667dc0023925d1e151","tid":1531402,"uid":46781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"有見及尋日和你塞嘅巴打講到Set Roadblock，我都有少少少少意見想提出下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （非割蓆 只係提出意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實set roadblock我都覺得可免則免，好多時手足喺重有車等出時就直接地block咗條路，但後面重有啲車排緊等出...<br />\n除咗巴士中咗roadblock會願意停車，其他司機真係有機會嬲同無奈到鬧人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發覺手足比較常喺路口前嘅直路set roadblock...但...咁架車都已經揸到入黎...你又唔俾第條路佢走....好似逼咗佢入條盲腸咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似近排去多咗嘅觀塘，啲車出迴旋處無任何指示話唔可以入觀塘道，但臨去到巴士站先發現封咗路（<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色XX</span> set喺路口前），佢入唔到巴士站、但又無路走、又難啲調頭。 <br />\n如果喺<span style=\"color: purple;\">紫色XX</span>嘅前面set roadblock ，咁就應該唔會有車再被困死<br />\n示意圖：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHjAtuF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHjAtuF.png&h=db26b288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信手足想做嘅係禁止狗增援，不過困住啲司機唔俾佢走好似唔係最好做法<br />\n<br />\n非司機，純粹拋磚等多啲專業人士提出辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eebf1f155e2fdf101e7ed8a33d5bebf3efa241f","tid":1531402,"uid":46781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:13:30.000Z","msg":"//轉//<br />\n<br />\n9月8日：<br />\n美國人權及民主法案大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1530650</a><br />\n時間：開放討論<br />\n地點：開放討論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9月13日：<br />\n各區同慶賀中秋<br />\n<br />\n9月14日：<br />\n中學生螢火之荊集會<br />\n主辦：凝火之聲 Youthire（不反對通知書申請中）<br />\n時間：16:00 - 21:00<br />\n地點：黃大仙廣場<br />\n<br />\n9月15日：<br />\n開放討論<br />\n<br />\n9月22日：<br />\n開放討論<br />\n<br />\n9月29日：<br />\n抗中共反納粹全球集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1511138/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1511138/page/1</a><br />\n時間：開放討論<br />\n地點：開放討論<br />\n<br />\n10月1日：<br />\n開放討論"},{"pid":"64bf6816243e27084bda28f6ee24770732f551c8","tid":1531402,"uid":46781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:15:12.000Z","msg":"和理非，好無力，好忟？<br />\n要抗爭，只有十月一前每日堅持做以下既事，係堅持，堅唔到都要堅，係呢到發誓你堅持呢個九月，就一個月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 罷消費（任何福建幫、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、藍紅食店）好難？勇武難唔難？<br />\n2. 低享樂（要發洩，做運動、十點9叫、唔好taobao消費食好野）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 每日like and share 1個文宣post<br />\n5. 下載Twitter 開acc,每日出1個post<br />\n6. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣教育自由行。<br />\n7. 每星期去連儂貼3張文宣<br />\n8. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n9. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n10. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n11. Tag或吹你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n<br />\n諗到再加，如果你咁都做唔到，講咩野好忟好惱無野可做。<br />\n只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"1b51f70f6bc6d30448b068f08a4cc33f069e1ea9","tid":1531402,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:15:40.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35008fb0f8c476743179d3c11d21d6ad5e56648","tid":1531402,"uid":46781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dDjMEfx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdDjMEfx.jpg&h=4a1d21b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba20d0b794be5f3b2d95922a10040dc9cc3a5ac6","tid":1531402,"uid":46781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5117a3be09f07e2d768554ec0e20c3fd75da66e3","tid":1531402,"uid":46781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:25:42.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a47551628eff9b07ed94f72e05ea409b26227243","tid":1531402,"uid":46781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:25:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0b430b3fad8f98100ba29e2ea886decabfed468","tid":1531402,"uid":46781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:26:04.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"bdafe10deae02bae60d9d17cdbe8af6826163d6e","tid":1531402,"uid":46781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:26:21.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"b9ab0594edca4947aa485bbb039d23b60ee9a5da","tid":1531402,"uid":46781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:26:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a64aea7ad3162f455473d1ba57bbacf5085d11d6","tid":1531402,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:41:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f46c95159